            "title": "Blocks and chains : introduction to Bitcoin, cryptocurrencies, and their consensus mechanisms",
            "abstract": [
                "7. Conclusion and open challenges -- 7.1 Conclusion -- A. Glossary -- Bibliography -- Authors&apos; biographies",
